July 28, 2017 11:10 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Sandell Asset Management Corp.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Sandell Asset Management Corp. is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to pooled investment vehicles. It also caters to insurance companies. The firm also manages separate client-focused portfolios. It invests in the public equity and fixed income markets across the globe. The firm conducts in-house research to make its investments. Sandell Asset Management Corp. was founded in 1998 and is based in New York City.


540 Madison Avenue36th FloorNew York, NY 10022United StatesFounded in 1998



Phone: 212-603-5700

Fax: 212-603-5710

www.sandellmgmt.com







