Funds






Funds


MLIS Castlerigg Equity Event and Arbitrage UCITS Fund

			PLEASE BE ADVISED that it has come to our attention that a fraudulent website has been created which is misrepresenting the name of Castlerigg UCITS Fund plc.  The website http://www.castlerigginvestments.com is NOT affiliated with any of Sandell Asset Management Corp.’s Castlerigg investment products, and has been identified as a scam.  See https://www.scamwarners.com/forum/viewtopic.php?f=10&p=255706.
			
			As of March 2014, Castlerigg UCITS Fund plc merged onto a Luxembourg UCITS platform, and has since received its Notice of Revocation of Authorization from the Central Bank of Ireland and is currently in liquidation.
		




Fund Description
Launched in October, 2010, the Castlerigg Merger Arbitrage and Equity Event UCITS Fund (an Irish authorized UCITS fund, IN LIQUIDATION), was formed to invest in equity special situations such as restructurings, recapitalizations and spinoffs, and merger arbitrage, including announced mergers, hostile and unsolicited transactions. The Fund's objective was to attain consistent capital growth over time, largely independent of market movements. In an effort to meet this objective, the Fund’s strategy is to seek to produce consistent, positive returns with low downside volatility. Capital has been allocated opportunistically and is totally fluid, resulting in ever-changing geographical exposures and strategy allocations within the firm's defined specialties.
As of 14-March 2014, Castlerigg UCITS Fund plc (the “Fund”) merged onto a Luxembourg UCITS platform, and is now available as the Merrill Lynch Investment Solutions – Castlerigg Equity Event and Arbitrage UCITS Fund.  The investment strategy and objectives of the Fund remain the same.  Details regarding Merrill Lynch Investment Solutions and the Fund are available at www.funds-invest.baml.com.
Central Bank of Ireland Notice of Revocation of Authorization
UK Reporting Funds Report
The Castlerigg Merger Arbitrage and Equity Event UCITS Fund (the “Castlerigg UCITS Fund”) is no longer available for direct investment. The information provided by following the link above is posted as part of continuing regulatory obligations, and does not constitute an offer to sell, or a solicitation of an offer to purchase, any interest in the Castlerigg UCITS Fund or any other investment product. 










© 2017 Sandell Castlerigg Investments. All rights reserved.Sandell Asset Management Europe Ltd. is authorised and regulated in the UK by the Financial Conduct Authority.
					
					
